title: Semplice X
description:
Hey friends

A little over 2 years we launched Semplice, and since much has changed and we kept working on our current version to improve it even further over the years.

But what I'm showing you here is something new, something completely new we've been working on for around a year now and we're coming very close to completion.

I won't say too much yet, but we're pretty excited and nervous already to share it with you.

For those of you who have been using Semplice for a while, you will be certainly one of the first to know about this new product launch.

Enjoy your weekend & Thanks again for all the supporting over the last couple years. Without you we wouldn't be able to do what we're doing right now, and I'm pretty impressed everyday to see what people build with Semplice.

Catching up soon with some more sneak peeks

Stay awesome
Tobias
